<br>
&quot;The path of righteousness leads the good man to do evil things.&quot;<br>
<br>
Saw that in a restroom in a bookstore in Montclair. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~andersonrob/LasSig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->andersonrob@earthlink.net<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->http://home.earthlink.net/~andersonrob/index.html<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->EverQuest: Lasgalen Lothir, Firiona Vie server<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->&quot;I'm not your bitch, don't hang your shit on me.&quot;  -Madonna, &quot;Human Nature&quot;</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=maritzia>Maritzia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Uptight Cleric</span><br>  Posts: 878<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/21/03 12:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1570.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: An interesting grafitto</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>&quot;The path of righteousness leads the good man to do evil things.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Probably a more accurate saying would be &quot;The Path to Righteousness can tempt the good man to do evil things.&quot;<br>
<br>
Or something like that, anyway.  Because if the good man does evil things, he has obviously strayed from the path of righteousness.  One thing I've never understood about many of my faith is that in their striving for so-called righteousness, they loose their compassion and mercy, which should be hallmarks of our faith.<br>
<br>
